data.description: A RARE opportunity to live in Canton's sought after Fairways of Pheasant Run subdivision. Nestled in this premiere golf course, is a stately colonial ready for you to make home.  This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath boasts a generously sized family room, with gas fireplace and tons of natural light. A beautifully redone kitchen with granite counter tops, perfect for entertaining, and then thru the sliding glass doors: an enclosed porch that offers privacy and relaxation. Up the winding staircase to the second floor, you'll find 3 generously sized bedrooms, and finally the primary suite, offering two walk in closets, a luxurious bathroom with a specialized tub perfect for soaking and relaxing after a long day. The unfinished lower level offers an additional 1500 sq ft. giving you the opportunity to finish it the way you'd like. This gorgeous home has many updates including: Kitchen ('10), Roof ('11), Windows ('14), Water Heater ('20), Furnace ('22). Located in a beautiful community near parks, shops, schools, restaurants and freeways. Don't miss out on the chance to own this well cared for home!
